annonstext:
If you are considering the challenge of a new role in a rapidly growing global company, this is an excellent opportunity to become a part of a great team with scope for long-term opportunity and rewards. Huawei is growing quickly and this professional role will have a strong presence. We are offering a challenging position and the opportunity to grow with us.

The Swedish Huawei Enterprise team is currently growing by over 35% year over year and we are looking for even more talents!

We are now looking for a Junior Account Manager (Consultant position) to join our Enterprise team.

Responsibilities:

- Ability to insight customers' strategies, businesses, and operation regarding to ICT area;
- Research and identify potential key customers and continue to expand and invest in;
- Cooperate with local channel partners to develop customer relationships and bidding tender.
- Planning and implementing communication with customers, understanding customer requirements and able to guide the customer requirements;

Requirements:

- Sales sense, able to develop sales opportunities;
- Good communication skill, team work spirit and strong work responsibility;
- Prefer have IT or technical related educational background
- Familiar with the use of various Microsoft office software
- Chinese as a native language, Fluent in English

